cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper deals with cross-language word embeddings, which is a topic related to natural language processing (NLP). Therefore, cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves evaluating the performance of different models, which falls under the scope of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of human references as ground truth, which is related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
